{"tid":498591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿電話網速慢　大陸仔鬧事打傷5警　被噴椒制服","createTime":"2017-12-14T02:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T05:17:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c020e1ccaa0d61a52f837096a5fae8c332947004","tid":498591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171214/s00001/3c6cc802dab62a9e1531f688f20f4945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F3c6cc802dab62a9e1531f688f20f4945.jpg&h=846d58a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅磡發生襲警案。昨晚8時許，有市民報警指，一名男子於土瓜灣道247B號一電訊公司與職員發生爭執，數名警員到場了解及調停，其間男子不合作，情緒激動，在店內大吵大鬧，更發難徒手襲擊5名警員。警員給予口頭警告不果，最後以胡椒噴劑將男子制服，男子被4名警員抬上警車。<br />\n <br />\n警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌「襲警」及「拒捕」罪名拘捕涉事的44歲姓黃男子，案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進。至凌晨1時許，5名受傷警員及被捕男子，同被送到伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被捕男子是新移民，早前由中國移居本港，去年獲得香港身分證。他昨晚到電訊公司，向職員投訴上網速度太慢，職員曾解釋因他使用的是5GB流量計劃，使用逾5GB數據後網速會按「公平使用原則」而自動減慢，但他不滿並與職員爭執。"},{"pid":"bc8321771295be31a20f96811b176fe5265e51a2","tid":498591,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:49:57.000Z","msg":"打打打打打"},{"pid":"804bb58ee6ebaa037a09c9812c291f35605999fa","tid":498591,"uid":12712,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:50:43.000Z","msg":"啲支那人係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75ad41bf0bb3aea710108152cbe11f044c98e08","tid":498591,"uid":62532,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"一惡治一惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d192a65de0159a6e70d2bd14afc2886a4059af","tid":498591,"uid":31637,"lik